-- KKR "moving ahead" on IPO, no comment on timing
-- 
-- Thu Nov 13, 2008 9:19am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/11/13/us-kkr-idUSTRE4AC4H820081113

 

 HONG KONG  (Reuters) - Kohlberg Kravis Roberts & Co KKR.UL co-founder George Roberts said the firm is "moving ahead with its IPO" but declined to comment on timing. 

 Asked if he could comment on the IPO, Roberts told Reuters, "Not really, other than the public statements we've made, which is we're moving ahead with it." Roberts spoke to Reuters after giving a speech at a private equity industry dinner in Hong Kong. (Reporting by  Jeffrey Hodgson ; Editing by Steve Orlofsky)